SEMDL Help Topic: reference extract

Usage:
- `ssd extract --out <output.ssd> --embed-provider ollama --embed-model <model> <input.ssd>`
- `ssd extract --stdout --embed-provider ollama --embed-model <model> <input.ssd>`

Status:
- This subcommand currently supports explicit Ollama-backed embedding generation from an existing `.ssd` input.
- Raw input extraction and non-Ollama providers remain planned but not implemented in the current slice.

Related help:
- `ssd help grammar`
- `ssd help troubleshooting`
